            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              Determine the range of the function <m>f</m>.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Let <m>\mathbb{R}^* = \left\{ { {x \in \mathbb{R}} \mid x \geq 0} \right\}</m>,
          and let <m>s\x \mathbb{R} \to \mathbb{R}^*</m> be defined by <m>s( x ) = x^2</m>.
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>
                Evaluate <m>s( { - 3} ), s( { - 1} ), s( 1 ), \text{ and } s( 3 )</m>.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                Determine the set of all of the preimages of 0 and the set of all preimages of 2.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
